"ובחירת :guilabel:`ברקוד`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:158
msgid ""
"Select an existing packaging, or create a new one by "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`. Be sure to specify the product, its packaging, and "
"the :guilabel:`Contained Quantity`. Specify whether it is available "
"for :guilabel:`Sales` or :guilabel:`Purchase`. Specify a :guilabel:`Barcode`."
