msgstr "מדפסת Zebra ZD411 עובדת הכי טוב להדפסת תוויות מ-Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration.rst:90
msgid ""
"For label printers, Odoo recommends the `Zebra ZD411 <https://www.zebra.com/"
"us/en/products/spec-sheets/printers/desktop/zd411-series.html>`__, as Odoo "
