msgstr ":guilabel:`מחיר קבוע`: `200`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:66
msgid ":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: :guilabel:`Furniture Delivery (manual)`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`מוצר משלוח`: :guilabel:`Furniture Delivery (manual)`"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:0
msgid "Set up a delivery method with a fixed price of 200."
msgstr "הגדירו שיטת משלוח במחיר קבוע של 200."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:73
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Availability` tab to define conditions for the delivery "
"method based on the order's content or destination:"
msgstr ""
"השתמש בכרטיסייה :guilabel:`זמינות` כדי להגדיר תנאים לשיטת המשלוח בהתבסס על "
"תוכן ההזמנה או יעדה:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:76
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Countries`: Specify one or more countries where the method is "
"available."
msgstr ":guilabel:`מדינות`: ציין מדינה אחת או יותר שבהן השיטה זמינה."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:77
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Max Weight`: Set a maximum weight; the method is only available "
"for orders below this limit."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`משקל מרבי`: הגדר משקל מרבי; השיטה זמינה רק להזמנות מתחת למגבלה זו."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Max Volume`: Set a maximum volume; the method is only available "
"for orders below this limit."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`נפח מרבי`: הגדר נפח מרבי; השיטה זמינה רק להזמנות מתחת למגבלה זו."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:81
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Must Have Tags`: The method is available only if at least one "
