#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/print_on_validation.rst:45
msgid ""
"After :ref:`enabling the Delivery Slip setting <inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"print_setup>` in the :guilabel:`Hardware` tab configuration options, "
"clicking :guilabel:`Validate` on the desired operation type downloads a PDF "
