msgstr ""
"בלשונית :guilabel:`SendCloud Configuration` של הטופס :guilabel:`New Shipping "
"Method`, לחץ על הקישור :guilabel:`Load your SendCloud shipping products`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/sendcloud_shipping.rst:165
